  "title": "Visitor Experience Associate (Part Time Staff for Navy Museum)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Visitor interaction, providing information and assistance</li>\n  <li>To assist Navy Museum staff members on the daily Museum operations</li>\n  <li>To assist Museum staff members to facilitate school and public programmes</li>\n  <li>Will be trained to provide information about the exhibits</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>An interest and passion for Singapore history, museums and the local art scene is an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Self-directed learner and problem solver who remains productive under pressure</li>\n  <li>Proficient in spoken and written English</li>\n  <li>Cultural understanding and empathy for diverse communities</li>\n  <li>Service oriented and enjoy interacting with people</li>\n  <li>Must be willing to work at Navy Museum Singapore, Address: 112 Tanah Merah Coast Road</li>\n  <li>Must be able to work on at least 1 weekend (Saturday or Sunday) every week</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Part-Time rate of $12/hour</strong></li>\n  <li>Uniform provided.</li>\n  <li>Transport provided at EXPO MRT on Sat/Sun and Public Holidays</li>\n  <li>Free SDC Adventurer Membership after 1 month deployment</li>\n</ul>",
